---
title: Prosciutto-Wrapped Chicken with Baked Mushroom Risotto & Rocket Salad
description: You deserve something special! Like this next-level meal with chicken breast wrapped in prosciutto; the cured meat holds in moisture and adds an abundance of flavour. Then, add a bed of mushroom-infused risotto and sharp Parmesan for a true gold star experience.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67158128ffa4e28ccb95b07d-069a3c0c.jpeg
